      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of early 20th century American and European film stills and photography from 1839 to the mid-twentieth century.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged by country. Film stills sub-divided by title. Photography sub-divided by artist name.</p>  
      </arrangement>
